{"tid":2322441,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"損失慘重｜老婦57萬私己錢藏鐵罐　慘遭蟲蛀　銀紙碎成碎片","createTime":"2020-12-12T10:27:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T10:36:41.000Z","uid":261647,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0ece9cba6d325c337ddacc7e56b43e48c8c7820f","tid":2322441,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T10:27:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2824869/損失慘重｜老婦57萬私己錢藏鐵罐 慘遭蟲蛀銀紙碎成碎片\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2824869%2F%E6%90%8D%E5%A4%B1%E6%85%98%E9%87%8D%EF%BD%9C%E8%80%81%E5%A9%A657%E8%90%AC%E7%A7%81%E5%B7%B1%E9%8C%A2%E8%97%8F%E9%90%B5%E7%BD%90%20%E6%85%98%E9%81%AD%E8%9F%B2%E8%9B%80%E9%8A%80%E7%B4%99%E7%A2%8E%E6%88%90%E7%A2%8E%E7%89%87&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=c6fc1eaf\" target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2824869/損失慘重｜老婦57萬私己錢藏鐵罐 慘遭蟲蛀銀紙碎成碎片</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CWWeRwJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCWWeRwJ.png&h=991cf070&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n老一輩的人愛用月餅罐等鐵盒存放貴重物品，惟儲存方式不當可能引發悲劇。馬來西亞有老婦以鐵罐收藏「私己錢」，多年後重新打開卻驚覺鐵罐遭害蟲入侵，當中銀紙被蛀至破損，最嚴重者甚至被蛀成碎片恐無法使用。<br />\n<br />\n私己錢藏鐵罐多年 一開驚揭遭蟲蛀<br />\n<br />\n綜合當地傳媒報道，馬來西亞一名華裔老婦以鐵罐藏起總數約30萬令吉（約57萬港元）多年，至近期後輩代為處理時才發現鐵罐已遭害蟲入侵，當中銀紙慘被蟲蛀導致面目全非。"},{"pid":"3b64b2628d5838ee3594bc11f60313b01988308e","tid":2322441,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T10:30:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a4fa23642907d90462859e742b9da368a38c7e6","tid":2322441,"uid":284432,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T10:31:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9ee76d981879d5a9cbc527402bd8ddd8f1ee8b2","tid":2322441,"uid":39838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T10:31:27.000Z","msg":"儲埋啲錢唔用有咩意思<br />\n收到咁埋連數錢嘅快感都無"},{"pid":"0ce1938f1f22d0ba310ef8a67bae82b702d15b01","tid":2322441,"uid":253016,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T10:31:28.000Z","msg":"達爾文的懲罰"},{"pid":"1911e8d68985a9f7463dcada4cb028aa8d9e76b4","tid":2322441,"uid":132810,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T10:31:47.000Z","msg":"老實講，明知有咁多錢，間唔時都要攞嚟CHECK下啦<br />\nbtw可能變舊炒，唔知有冇得用"},{"pid":"ff57ab7f5986abe9a2dcdc6abd81d267a3b0f3bd","tid":2322441,"uid":249242,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T10:33:53.000Z","msg":"Check check 床下底d美金"},{"pid":"a2d914fe2178e99bded01c626edcd5a830b34bf3","tid":2322441,"uid":63934,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T10:34:34.000Z","msg":"唔係燒到變焦炭應該銀行換過無難度"},{"pid":"3a1564262d933f5eb4159cafc35a35193af9f17b","tid":2322441,"uid":249242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1911e8d68985a9f7463dcada4cb028aa8d9e76b4","tid":2322441,"uid":132810,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T10:31:47.000Z","msg":"老實講，明知有咁多錢，間唔時都要攞嚟CHECK下啦<br />\nbtw可能變舊炒，唔知有冇得用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T10:35:11.000Z","msg":"唔知柒婆點check 咁多現金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e40ec5a5b8a80b6713358656ea50b4aa676d2b20","tid":2322441,"uid":132810,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3a1564262d933f5eb4159cafc35a35193af9f17b","tid":2322441,"uid":249242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1911e8d68985a9f7463dcada4cb028aa8d9e76b4","tid":2322441,"uid":132810,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T10:31:47.000Z","msg":"老實講，明知有咁多錢，間唔時都要攞嚟CHECK下啦<br />\nbtw可能變舊炒，唔知有冇得用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T10:35:11.000Z","msg":"唔知柒婆點check 咁多現金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj